If I pass out,

17
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:35,760
Hotel Rafflesia will stop...

18
00:01:37,570 --> 00:01:45,090
Every little bit of damage counts...

19
00:01:50,690 --> 00:01:56,000
I can still fight...

20
00:01:57,070 --> 00:02:00,530
I can still...

21
